N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 20 ยง 263.11 - Preparation of City of Yonkers earnings tax returns

State Regulations

The provisions of section
151.15
of this Title, with respect to the preparation of New York State income tax
returns, shall also be applicable to the preparation of City of Yonkers
earnings tax returns. Notes
